# Docker

- Base image: `node:20-alpine`, multi-stage build
- `mariadb-client` provides `mysqldump` in container
- Backup output: `/var/db_backups` (bind-mount to host `./db_backups`)
- SQLite persistence: named volume `sqlite-data` mounted at `/app/data`
- `SQLITE_DB_PATH` env override in compose: `/app/data/mysql-maintainer.db`
- MySQL healthcheck required before app starts (`depends_on: condition: service_healthy`)
